subject: Dear Sir
body:
Dear Sir
How are you doing today?Hope you are doing well
I have a business proposal that may interest you.
kindly reply back so that i will send your further details about the proposal.
waiting for your urgent response
Regards
Nana owusu

subject: Re:   Dear Sir
body:
Hello Nana Owusu,

I hope this message finds you well. I'm intrigued by your business proposal and would love to hear more about it. Could you please provide me with some more details? 

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Lupe
